ZH: 今天的天气很凉爽。
EN: The weather is very cool today.

ZH: 暴风雨过后，空气变得清新凉爽。
EN: After the storm, the air becomes fresh and cool.

ZH: 前几天的凉爽天气让人感到舒适。
EN: The cool weather a few days ago was very comfortable.

ZH: 山间的清晨总是特别凉爽。
EN: The mornings in the mountains are always especially cool.

ZH: 晨跑是在凉爽天气中运动的好时机。
EN: Morning runs are a good time to exercise in cool weather.

ZH: 晚上的凉爽气候适合散步。
EN: The cool weather at night is perfect for a walk.

ZH: 在湖边的草地上躺着，感受凉爽的微风。
EN: Lying on the grass by the lake, feeling the cool breeze.

ZH: 凉爽的夜晚让人睡得很香。
EN: Cool nights make people sleep well.

ZH: 山上的气温凉爽是因为海拔高。
EN: The cool temperature on the mountain is due to its high altitude.

ZH: 他喜欢早晨的凉爽气候。
EN: He enjoys the cool weather in the morning.

ZH: 到公园里散步，感受凉爽的风。
EN: Take a walk in the park and feel the cool breeze.

ZH: 乘凉爽的天气去爬山是一种享受。
EN: Climbing a mountain in cool weather is a pleasure.

ZH: 游泳池周围的凉爽气温让游客感到惬意。
EN: The cool temperature around the swimming pool makes the guests feel comfortable.

ZH: 天气凉爽时，大家喜欢在户外野餐。
EN: People enjoy picnics outdoors when the weather is cool.

ZH: 凉爽的天气适合种植一些寒冷作物。
EN: Cool weather is suitable for growing some cold crops.

ZH: 冬天的阳光虽然凉爽，但看起来很温暖。
EN: The winter sun may be cool, but it looks warm.

ZH: 阴雨的天气让人感到凉爽而舒适。
EN: The rainy weather makes people feel cool and comfortable.

ZH: 与好友一起乘着凉爽的微风去郊游。
EN: Go on an outing with friends in the cool breeze.

ZH: 凉爽的气温使得户外运动更加有趣。
EN: The cool temperature makes outdoor sports more enjoyable.

ZH: 在凉爽的天气中，看电影是一种放松的方式。
EN: Watching a movie is a relaxing way to spend time in cool weather.
